The '''''Fury''''' was a [[Corsair battleship]] that saw service in the [[Navy/Legends|navy]] of the [[Brotherhood of Darkness/Legends|Brotherhood of Darkness]] during the [[New Sith Wars]] along with its sister ship, [[Rage (corsair battleship)|''Rage'']]. While its crew was controlled by [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Skere Kaan|Kaan's]] [[Battle meditation/Legends|battle meditation]], it was still destroyed in the [[First Battle of Ruusan]] in [[1002 BBY]].

